==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fanfoot
<hw>Fan"foot`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>A species of gecko having the toes expanded into large
lobes for adhesion. The Egyptian fanfoot (<spn>Phyodactylus gecko</spn>)
is believed, by the natives, to have venomous toes.</def> <sd>(b)</sd>
<def>Any moth of the genus <gen>Polypogon</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fang</ent>⟦br⟧
